{
  "_comment": [
    "Balatro DQN \u2014 Joker definitions.",
    "",
    "Each joker has three parts:",
    "  trigger   : when the effect fires",
    "              'passive'        \u2014 always active, added every hand",
    "              'on_hand_played' \u2014 fires once per hand play if condition met",
    "              'on_card_scored' \u2014 fires once per qualifying scored card",
    "",
    "  condition : what must be true for the trigger to fire",
    "              {'type': 'none'}                         \u2014 always fires",
    "              {'type': 'hand_contains', 'hand_type': X} \u2014 played hand contains pattern X",
    "              {'type': 'hand_type_exact', 'hand_type': X} \u2014 played hand is exactly X",
    "              {'type': 'card_count_le',  'value': N}   \u2014 N or fewer cards played",
    "              {'type': 'card_suit',      'suit': X}    \u2014 card suit matches X (S/H/D/C)",
    "",
    "  effect    : what the joker does when triggered",
    "              {'type': 'add_mult',  'value': N} \u2014 adds N to multiplier",
    "              {'type': 'add_chips', 'value': N} \u2014 adds N to chips",
    "",
    "Tiers:",
    "  1 \u2014 simple hand-type conditional or passive (phases 6-7)",
    "  2 \u2014 per-card suit or count conditional (phase 8+)"
  ],
